sequenceDiagram
 participant User
 participant Angular as Angular App
 participant Guard as Route Guard
 participant Service as Weather Service
 participant HTTP as HTTP Client
 participant API as .NET API
 participant Controller as Weather Controller
 participant BizService as Weather Service (BE)
 participant Repository as Weather Repository
 participant Dapper as Dapper ORM
 participant DB as SQLite Database
 
 User->>Angular: Navigate to Weather Page
 Angular->>Guard: Check Route Access
 Guard-->>Angular: Access Granted
 
 Angular->>Service: Request Weather Data
 Service->>HTTP: HTTP GET /api/weather
 HTTP->>API: HTTPS Request
 
 API->>Controller: Route to WeatherController
 Controller->>BizService: Call GetWeatherAsync()
 BizService->>Repository: Call GetAllWeatherAsync()
 Repository->>Dapper: Execute SQL Query
 Dapper->>DB: SELECT * FROM Weather
 
 DB-->>Dapper: Return Data Rows
 Dapper-->>Repository: Return Weather Entities
 Repository-->>BizService: Return Weather List
 BizService-->>Controller: Return Weather DTOs
 Controller-->>API: Return HTTP 200 + JSON
 
 API-->>HTTP: HTTPS Response
 HTTP-->>Service: Observable<Weather[]>
 Service->>Angular: Update Signal State
 Angular->>User: Display Weather Data
 
 Note over Angular, DB: Error Handling
 alt Error Occurs
 DB-->>Dapper: Database Error
 Dapper-->>Repository: Exception
 Repository-->>BizService: Repository Exception
 BizService-->>Controller: Service Exception
 Controller-->>API: HTTP 500 Error
 API-->>HTTP: Error Response
 HTTP-->>Service: HTTP Error
 Service->>Angular: Update Error Signal
 Angular->>User: Display Error Message
 end